[{"name":"Adding and Modifying Elements in Array ","code":"*our objective is to add an additional number at the end of an array*
```
int numbers [] = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6}; //initial array
int numbersTwo [] = new int[7]; //create an array with one additional position
for(int x = 0; x < numbers.length(); x++)
{
     numbersTwo[x] = numbers[x];
}
numbersTwo[6] = 7;

```
*modifying an element in a position*
```
numbers[4] = 9;
